 248:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal.c ****   *       The SysTick interrupt must have higher priority (numerically lower)
 249:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal.c ****   *       than the peripheral interrupt. Otherwise the caller ISR process will be blocked.
 250:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal.c ****   *       The function is declared as __weak  to be overwritten  in case of other
